  m_text: "Tento projekt byl vytvo\u0159en v r\xE1mci p\u0159edm\u011Btu Game Development
    I na FI MU.\n\nAutor v\u0161eho, co nen\xED n\xED\u017Ee uvedeno: Jan Kubala\n\nZvuk
    st\u0159elby: https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/clean-machine-gun-burst-98224\n\nHudba
    v pozad\xED: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5EYX8l-OJqE\n\nZvuk zni\u010Den\xED
    nep\u0159\xE1tel:\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IKDrqkFBNmo\nhttps://www.myinstants.com/en/search/?name=Blyaaaa\n\nObr\xE1zky
    vylep\u0161en\xED:\nhttps://ww1.habsburger.net/en/media/crew-machine-gun-schwarzlose-austro-hungarian-infantry-field-title-page-oesterreichische\nhttps://www.popularmechanics.com/military/news/a22633/forgotten-weapons-folding-body-armor\n\nObr\xE1zky
    a zvuk z filmu:\nhttps://prehraj.to/dobry-vojak-svejk-a-poslusne-hlasim-hd-16-9/684f0861e22c5\n\nPozad\xED
    v levelech:\nhttps://www.dreamstime.com/seamless-pattern-forest-top-view-map-above-hand-drawn-green-park-background-trees-aerial-pov-image338545226\nhttps://www.dreamstime.com/seamless-pattern-forest-top-view-map-above-hand-drawn-green-park-background-trees-aerial-pov-good-web-print-image318989876"
